        "title": "Intro",
        "content": [
                    "<p>When working with jQuery, would you prefer doing</p>",
                    "<pre data-brush=\"Xml\">&lt;a href=\"#\" onclick=\"someFunction();return false;\"&gt;test&lt;/a&gt;</pre>",
                    "<p>Or do something like this</p>",
                    "<pre data-brush=\"JScript\">$(function() {",
                    "   $('a').click(function() {",
                    "       someFunction();",
                    "       return false;",
                    "   });",
                    "});</pre>",
                    "<p>I would personally without doubt choose the latter, this is how I love using jQuery.",
                    "Listening to events and modifying the DOM externally from an included script file.</p>",
                    "<p>Now how do you do your server side templating?",
                    "I bet you do something like this (<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/guide/6.%20The%20Web%20Layer.html#6.2 Groovy Server Pages\" target=\"_blank\">GSP</a>):",
                    "<pre data-brush=\"Xml\">",
                    "&lt;html&gt;",
                    "   &lt;body&gt;",
                    "       Hello ${params.name}&lt;br&gt;",
                    "       &lt;g:each in=\"${[1,2,3]}\" var=\"num\"&gt;",
                    "           &lt;p&gt;Number ${num}&lt;/p&gt;",
                    "       &lt;/g:each&gt;",
                    "   &lt;/body&gt;",
                    "&lt;/html&gt;"
                   ]
